{"tid":1038985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孩童增進大人幸福感？研究：取決於你有沒有錢","createTime":"2019-02-27T06:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T09:01:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"934dcd25fe1dd01724e5eb394cf0c885d28b961a","tid":1038985,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"孩童總是為大人帶來歡樂？一項新研究卻顯示，歡樂的前提可能是父母必須「夠有錢」。<br />\n美國國家經濟研究所（National Bureau of Economic Research）研究指出，當家長陷入財務困難時，孩童反而是造成不開心的因素；相反地，如果財務狀況不成問題，則孩童能增加家長們的幸福感。<br />\n研究由達特茅斯學院（Dartmouth College）經濟學教授布蘭弗洛（David Blanchflower）和巴黎經濟學院（Paris School of Economics）教授克拉克（Andrew Clark）合力撰寫，分析從2009年至2018年，歐洲35國、100萬人口的生活滿意度調查。<br />\n布蘭弗洛直白地說，殘酷事實擺在眼前，只是之前沒有人發現：「只要孩童沒有對你繳帳單造成困擾，他們才會讓父母更快樂。」（林孝儒／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190227/640_866e71a4eb800d507a18631ed946cf88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190227%2F640_866e71a4eb800d507a18631ed946cf88.jpg&h=942a0411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190227/1524437/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190227%2F1524437%2F&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6VuZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=5b872519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190227%2F1524437%2F&h=7107ce53\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190227/1524437/</a>"},{"pid":"20d39b2f4178e1b534d2149b4428a519232d85cf","tid":1038985,"uid":49258,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:04:53.000Z","msg":"無仔女又有錢先最好, 廢鳩研究"},{"pid":"d6c9f8a23fcdc4e73e48b08a5fe731911dacdcdc","tid":1038985,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"香港冇孩子 = 冇公屋 = 租劏房 = 唔開心"},{"pid":"7960fe8627479972a23085402513731993